Class ThirdPartyBinaryNotFoundException

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ThirdPartyBinaryNotFoundException
extends java.util.MissingResourceException
    Exception to indicate that a 3rd party binary that is required by the code cannot be found. This usually indicates a setup issue.
